# FRONTEND DESIGN SYSTEM & UI RULES

## DESIGN TOKENS
- Primary: Earthy Green (`#2E7D32`)
- Secondary: Warm Orange (`#F57C00`)
- Cards: Pure White with `shadows.soft`.
- Hide all scrollbars globally (`showsVerticalScrollIndicator={false}`).

## TEMPLATE USAGE (MANDATORY)
- Never build a screen from scratch.
- Wrap multi-step forms in `WizardFlowTemplate`.
- Wrap basic views in `SimpleScreenTemplate`.
- Wrap dashboard views in `DashboardScreenTemplate`.

## MICRO-INTERACTIONS
- Use Skeleton loaders when fetching from Supabase.
- Add active states to Buttons and Selection Cards.
- Implement Toast/Alerts for success/error handling.
- Use `lucide-react` or `MaterialIcons` extensively.